messages.messageBody:
I have a few items in the "Lost & Found" box.

Please e-mail me privately if you'd lost one of them 'cause I've found 'em:

One pair shoes, blue zippered "sandals" with a white "10"

one dark purple/burgundy zippered "hoodie"

one small silver hairbrush

one pair Hannas (I'm envious! Cameron was always "hanna-ed" as a baby.)
multi-striped pants, size 80

a set: one pair purple boy's underwear, one pair blue shorts, one grey
"dragon" t-shirt

one disposable camera

one drumstick

and one leather cell-phone or walkie-talkie case that hooks to a belt

I'll post this on the message boards as well.

What isn't claimed, I'll bring to MA next year.

Thanks!

~Kelly
